<p>We are already in our final day of the conference. We hope you have had a great experience in the virtual platform. Although being in person would be ideal, we hope you have found additional benefits to being virtual. One of which is that the platform will remain open for 30 days! If you missed sessions, continue to login for &lsquo;on demand&rsquo; viewing.</p>
<p>Today kicks off with hearing from our <strong>Award Winners</strong>. We want to again extend our congratulations to the outstanding winners. Nominations open soon for the 2021 conference. Consider submitting a nomination!</p>
